headline: Gear Up for Eastman Chemical (EMN) Q1 Earnings: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for Eastman Chemical (EMN), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended March 2025.
